This is a map based of the show Bleach You start out buy a knife that makes u pick up your sword that cause 10 damage then you can also knife the enemy T's are spread out and CT are spawned on top of the rock -- there is a custom model for the sword u have *Note in one of my screen shots there is a custom player skin from my server that doesn't come with the map*

-------Added--------
+ Healing sword so u can heal teammates 1 healing sword per team all u do is point sword at them and that will heal can make some nice strats with this

+Also added 2 more battle zones from the show the front park added blood and stuff were ichigo fought renji and also added in the back were Yoruichi and Cpt. Soi Fong fought at  Forest like area with tree's

-------FIXED---------
The crash problem when u look straight up no longer crashes at all so don't have to worrie about that 

Also fixed the problem with the one sword that if u were to walk into it, it would also crash the server
